Preamble:
The Christian Software License (CSL) is a permissive open source license that seeks to promote the principles and values of the Christian faith within the realm of software development. 
This license is designed to encourage collaboration, sharing, and the propagation of software that aligns with Christian values, while respecting the rights and freedoms of developers and users.

By using, modifying, or distributing software licensed under the CSL, you agree to abide by the terms and conditions set forth in this license.

